Definition: marked by extreme intensity of emotions or convictions
Example: inclined to react violently; fervid; fierce loyalty; in a tearing rage; vehement dislike; violent passions
Synonyms: noun, attribute, fierceness, tearing, vehement, violent, trigger-happy, marked, by, extreme, intensity, of, emotions, or, convictions, inclined, to, react, violently, fervid, loyalty, in, a, rage, dislike, passions
Category: adj.all
